{"tid":1925324,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"海關拘捕4藥房負責人　涉售含菌量超標外科口罩","createTime":"2020-03-14T10:03:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T14:37:06.000Z","uid":51469,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"214ca5fe28e38c25bd6ef349b9e5ea524d68f1b1","tid":1925324,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T10:03:38.000Z","msg":"海關在4間分別位於銅鑼灣和灣仔的藥房拘捕4名負責人，他們出售4款含菌量超標的外科口罩，涉嫌違反消費品安全條例，有關口罩每盒價錢200至499元，其中兩款產地標示為尼泊爾和土耳其。<br />\n<br />\n海關消費者保障科首席貿易管制主任李民佳表示，早前試購的24款外科口罩經化驗後，發現其中4款含菌量超標最多超過11倍。他提醒市民，佩戴有關口罩可能令皮膚不適，或者令氣管受感染： <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1514469-20200314.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1514469-20200314.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=mMkNc61%2FAm5nYK%2BypTXmCf%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=8cc9a513\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1514469-20200314.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=c8d86966\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1514469-20200314.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"297482f907296b0018001d8fc447ae32061fc532","tid":1925324,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T10:05:23.000Z","msg":"重判啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"4a3291f2faed1023cfcb204987e6606d69c277f2","tid":1925324,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"297482f907296b0018001d8fc447ae32061fc532","tid":1925324,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T10:05:23.000Z","msg":"重判啦屌你老母"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T10:10:48.000Z","msg":"藥房狗係抵撚死<br />\n真係無一間藥房會知自己賣緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c60bb4e83d901960d886698277c2170d9baa75a0","tid":1925324,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T10:31:15.000